I"o<p>I use S3 to host my site and the <a href="https://github.com/laurilehmijoki/s3_website">s3_website</a> plugin to deploy, if you don’t do both of these, delete the <code class="highlighter-rouge">s3_website.yml</code> file and edit the deploy raketask to fit your needs.</p>

<p>If you plan on using S3 make sure you edit the configs:</p>

<ul>
  <li>FIRST - add the s3_website.yml file to your gitignore so your credentials don’t end up on the web.</li>
  <li>s3_website.yml
    <ul>
      <li>add your <code class="highlighter-rouge">s3_id</code>. <code class="highlighter-rouge">s3_secret</code>, and <code class="highlighter-rouge">s3_bucket</code></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Update the Rakefile notify task to use your url
    <ul>
      <li>replace <code class="highlighter-rouge">site = "www.YOUR-URL.com"</code> with your actual url.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
:ET